17 of 1 percent of the fair market value of the motor vehicle and a local title ad valorem
18 tax fee in an amount equal to one-quarter of 1 percent of the fair market value of the
19 motor vehicle. Such title ad valorem tax fees shall be an alternative ad valorem tax as
20 authorized by Article VII, Section I, Paragraph III(b)(3) of the Georgia Constitution."
21 SECTION 2.
22 Said title is further amended in paragraph (6) of Code Section 48-13-50.2, relating to
23 definitions relative to excise tax on rooms, lodgings, and accommodations, by striking "or"
24 at the end of subparagraph (O), by replacing the period with "; and" at the end of
25 subparagraph (P), and by adding a new subparagraph to read as follows:
26 "(Q) Air service product expansion at air carrier airports."
27 SECTION 3.
28 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
